            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " stands out because it tackles the repetitive drudgery that eats into every professional's day. This isn't another chatbot—it's an autonomous agent that manages your inbox, calendar, and follow-ups while you focus on deep work. If you're curious about a real productivity upgrade, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "explore Lindy's features here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
