      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lindy's Standout New & Highlighted Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lindy consistently rolls out updates that feel genuinely useful, not gimmicky. The latest round has solidified it as a top-tier assistant.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Autonomous Multi-Channel Agents",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-lindy"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can now deploy specialized \"Lindys\" for specific tasks. One manages your CRM updates, another handles meeting prep and follow-ups, and a third drafts email responses. They work in parallel, 24/7, learning your preferences and tone over time. For a deeper dive into setting these up, check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Lindy tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Intelligent Meeting Scheduling & Notes",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tired of the back-and-forth to find a meeting time? Lindy integrates directly with your calendar and email to propose times, send invites, and even generate detailed notes and action items after the call. It's like having a dedicated assistant in every meeting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Seamless CRM Integration",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/lindy-use-cases"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is a game-changer for sales and account management. Lindy can log calls, update contact records, and draft follow-up emails based on your conversation notes—all without you lifting a finger. The time reclaimed here is massive. We break down more ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "creative use cases for Lindy",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " on TonyCiencia.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "100+ App Integrations",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lindy plays nicely with the tools you already use, from Slack and Gmail to HubSpot and Salesforce. This connectivity means it becomes a central hub for your workflow, not another siloed app.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
