        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Project Managers & Executives:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Keep projects moving and inboxes clean. Lindy's ability to summarize threads, track action items, and prepare you for meetings is invaluable for high-level oversight.",
