            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". It’s not a point solution; it’s a holistic assistant that understands context across your communication apps. It learns your style, anticipates needs based on calendar events, and works proactively. This isn't just about *doing* tasks; it's about *managing* workflows. We expand on this in our article ",
